uk.ac.cam.darknet.common

Class AttributeReliabilityPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.darknet.common.AttributeReliabilityPair

  • public class AttributeReliabilityPair
extends java.lang.Object
    This simple class is used to store an attribute with its reliability. This class is constructed only by the Properties class. When retrieving attributes, client code should cast it to an appropriate type (using the global attribute table), if needed.

    Ibtehaj Nadeem
